  "title": "Slow Simmered Saudi Arabian Russet Potato Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and comforting weeknight stew featuring russet potatoes and tempered spices, inspired by the flavors of Saudi Arabia, made with ayurvedic-rajasic friendly ingredients. This dish is perfect for a cold evening.",
