  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add the cumin seeds and coriander seeds and let them sizzle for a few seconds.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the cubed potatoes, turmeric, red chili powder, salt, and black pepper, and stir well.",
    "Add 2 cups of water to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let the stew simmer for 30 minutes, or until the potatoes are tender.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
